settings.heading: Johana K Hanson's professional photography services combine the classic knowledge of traditional photographic portraiture and lighting with an innovative and contemporary style. Our mission is to further develop the overall excellence of photography and to capture memories that will be cherished for a lifetime, in the timeless photographs, made thanks to and for the many souls that roam the Earth.
